---
title: Roasted Squash and Apple Salad with Arugula, Goat Cheese and Ginger-Vinaigrette
description: Get your fill of veggies with this hearty squash and apple salad! A ginger-spiked dressing and a touch of chili adds warmth to this winter salad.
